set_option_value

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_option_value -  This method sets an option value on the player.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int set_option_value(object player,
string path,
string value)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^player%^RESET%^ - the player to find the value on
%^BOLD%^path%^RESET%^ - the path to the option
%^BOLD%^value%^RESET%^ - the value directly from the command line

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/options_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets an option value on the player.
.EP

